###     KNOWLEDGE BASE BACKEND

```
backend/
│── app/
│   │── __init__.py        # app factory, db init, register blueprints
│   │── models.py          # SQLAlchemy models (Users, Articles, Categories)
│   │── routes/            
│   │    │── __init__.py   # blueprint registration
│   │    │── articles.py   # article routes
│   │    │── categories.py # category routes
│   │    │── users.py      # user routes (admin stuff)
│   │── seed.py            # seeding script
│   │── config.py          # DB configs, env handling
│
│── migrations/            # auto-generated by Flask-Migrate
│── venv/                  # virtual environment (gitignored)
│── .env                   # DB URL, secret keys
│── requirements.txt
│── run.py                 # entrypoint to start the app

 ```